      *OET do file
*By Phil Tian
*version 11.2

clear all

set mem 250m
set maxvar 32000
set matsize 2000
set more off

cd E:/
capture log close
log using "OET_log", replace
use oetaug2010_pitstoplevel_v8.dta, clear

gen double ps=psexpectation/1000
gen double y=ln(ps+0.000001/(1-ps+0.000001))

program define OET_ML

args lnf lngamma sigma fn
tempvar m
gen double `m'=y/exp(`lngamma')-winpc -`fn'
quietly replace `lnf'=ln(normalden(`m'/`sigma'))-ln(exp(`lngamma'))-ln(`sigma')
end

ml model lf OET_ML (lngamma:bet  sdwin  slostakes swealth BMI   malay international*  weekinc_2  wealth_1 wealth_2 perfuni  totalprpayout  lefthand  englishspeaker  experiment  mum_school dad_school  dad_qual  dad_hiqual SBI_anticipate SBI_moment opt04  opt06  depression alcohol_dummy happy  luckyans   relig vegi, noconstant) (sigma:) (fn:bet  sdwin  englishspeaker  mum_school dad_school  dad_qual SBI_reminisce SBI_anticipate  opt06  depression alcohol_dummy luckyans)  
ml search
ml check
ml maximize
ml graph

predict yhat
gen double e=y-yhat
histogram yhat, kdensity
graph export yhat.png, replace
histogram e, kdensity
graph export error.png, replace
